rComments: Very interesting and knowledgable professor, but the course itself is quite dry, so can't really blame him for lectures being rather boring.

Great Prof! The best in the finance department! Has a great sense of humour too,so no one falls asleep during the lectures("STANDARD & POOR - your life in a nutshell"."WINDOWS -- What you jump out of when you're the sucker who bought Yahoo @ $240 per share"). The tests and the grading are fair. Stick to his notes and you'll do very well.
